dures that are designed to ensure", "bbox": [164.3, 1011.7, 1135.7, 1033.3]}, {"text": "that information required to be disclosed in our reports under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended (the", "bbox": [89.3, 1035.8, 1059.7, 1056.6]}, {"text": "“Exchange Act”), is recorded, processed, summarized and reported within the time periods specified in the SEC’s rules and", "bbox": [89.3, 1059.6, 1124.5, 1080.5]}, {"text": "forms, and that such information is accumulated and communicated to management, including our Chief Executive Officer", "bbox": [89.3, 1083.6, 1120.9, 1104.5]}, {"text": "(“CEO”) and Chief Financial Officer (“CFO”), as appropriate, to allow timely decisions regarding required disclosure. In", "bbox": [89.3, 1107.7, 1106.3, 1128.5]}, {"text": "designing and evaluating the disclosure controls and procedures, management recognized that any controls and procedures,", "bbox": [89.3, 1131.5, 1122.6, 1152.4]}, {"text": "no matter how well designed and operated, can provide only reasonable assurance of achieving the desired control objectives,", "bbox": [89.3, 1155.5, 1143.1, 1176.4]}, {"text": "as ours are designed to do, and management necessarily was required to apply its judgment in evaluating the cost-benefit", "bbox": [89.3, 1179.6, 1102.2, 1200.4]}, {"text": "relationship of possible controls and procedures.", "bbox": [89.3, 1203.4, 504.0, 1224.3]}, {"text": "In connection with the preparation of this Annual Report on Form 10-K, as of December 31, 2008, an evaluation", "bbox": [164.3, 1248.2, 1109.1, 1269.1]}, {"text": "was performed under the supervision and with the participation of our management, including the CEO and CFO, of the", "bbox": [89.3, 1272.2, 1096.3, 1293.1]}, {"text": "effectiveness of our disclosure controls and procedures (as defined in Rule 13a-15(e) under the Exchange Act). Based on", "bbox": [89.3, 1296.2, 1103.1, 1317.1]}, {"text": "such evaluation, our CEO and CFO concluded that, as of December 31, 2008, our disclosure controls and procedures were", "bbox": [89.3, 1320.1, 1115.9, 1341.0]}, {"text": "effective.", "bbox": [89.3, 1344.1, 177.7, 1365.0]}, {"text": "There has been no change in our internal control over financial reporting during the quarter ended December 31,", "bbox": [164.3, 1388.9, 1107.5, 1409.7]}, {"text": "2008 that has materially affected, or is reasonably likely to materially affect, our internal control over financial reporting.", "bbox": [89.3, 1412.9, 1110.2, 1433.8]}]}